<HEADLINE> Simba FC Beats Dire Dawa Locomotive FC in African Soccer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, February 16 (Xinhua) -- Simba FC of Tanzania defeated
Dire Dawa Locomotive FC of Ethiopia 1-0 in the second leg match
of African football Conferation Cup soccer competitions In Addis
Ababa, Ethiopia on Sunday:
</P>
<P>
The Tanzanian team led 1-0 at halftime.
</P>
<P>
The match drew 15,000 spectators at the stadium.
</P>
<P>
Simba FC won the two-leg match 5-1 on aggregate. 
</P>
