<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, February 17 (Xinhua) -- The budget for the 1998 Winter
Olympic Games will top 100 billion yen (800 million U.S. dollars)
but it may be offset by the yen's depreciation which will boost
television rights and sponsorship deals, Nagano Olympics
organisers said on Monday.
</P>
