<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, February 17 (Xinhua) -- Palestinian National Authority
(PNA) President Yasser Arafat is expected to pay an official visit
to Turkey Thursday, Turkish Foreign Ministry Spokesman Omer Akbel
announced here today.
