<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, Februry 17 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today fell 13 HK dollars to close at 3,190 HK dollars a tael,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 345.56 US dollars a troy ounce,
down 1.38 US dollars at today's exchange rate of one US dollar to
7.7489 HK dollars.  
</P>
