counterpart Al Gore, opened in Cape Town today.
</P>
<P>
The session will review progress reports by six of the
Commission's sub-committee in the areas of investment and trade,
science and technology, human resources development ad education,
conservation and environment, agriculture, and sustainable
energy, a source said.
</P>
<P>
