personnel and is asking Chinese students studying abroad to return
to work there.
</P>
<P>
Statistics show that by the year 2000 the coastal city, located
in southern Guangdong province, will need a total of 206,000
high-level technicians, managers and administrators, meaning an
additional 120,000 people from 1996's figure.
</P>
