Fortunato Abat of the MILF's decision.
</P>
<P>
Some Army soldiers backed by helicopter gunships has conducted
offensives on February 6, 8 and 15 on some MILF positions in
Shariff Aguak town and nearby areas, Jaafar said.
</P>
<P>
The military offensives resulted in gunbattles with MILF rebels
and left some casualties, but Jaafar refused to give any specific
figures on the reported casualties. 
</P>
