<HEADLINE> Poland's Women Athletes to Run in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WARSAW, February 16 (Xinhua) -- Five runners was selected to
take part in a women's road relay race in Beijing next month
through a running competition, named "From Warsaw to Beijing" here
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The five qualified athletes in the 8-kilometer race were
Violetta Kryza, Justyna Bak, Renata Sobiesiak, Danuta Marczyk and
Joanna Gront.
</P>
<P>
