athletes through a sports event open to all people.
</P>
<P>
Some 100 runners took part in Sunday's race. The oldest
competitor is 74, while the youngest 14.
</P>
<P>
The annual Beijing International Women's Road Relay Race will
be staged on March 1 in the Chinese capital. 
</P>
